#### arrow functions

```javascript

  return x + y;
```

E o tal do contexto/escopo?

---

Com contexto

```javascript
var person = {
  name: 'Joao',
  age: 22,
  sayHello: function() {
    return `Hi, I'm ${this.name} and I'm ${this.age} years old`
  }
};

person.sayHello(); // Hi, I'm Joao and I'm 22 years old üëç
```

---

Sem contexto

```javascript
var person = {
  name: 'Joao',
  age: 22,
  sayHello: () => 
    `Hi, I'm ${this.name} and I'm ${this.age} years old`
};

person.sayHello(); 
//Hi, I'm undefined and I'm undefined years old üëé
```
---

### destructuring

```javascript
const [a, b, ...rest] = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] // Com valores

console.log(a) // 1
console.log(b) // 2
console.log(rest) // 3, 4, 5
```

```javascript
const person = { name: 'Joao', age: 22 } // Com objetos

const {name, age} = person

console.log(name) // 'Joao'
console.log(age) // 22
```

export default CodeSlide

```javascript
class Dialog {
  constructor(message = 'Sem mensagem ainda!') {
    this._message = message;
  }

  get message() {
    return this._message;
  }

  set message(message) {
    this._message = message;
  }

  show() {
    alert(this._message);
  }
}

const dlg = new Dialog();
dlg.show(); // Sem mensagem aidna!
```

---

#### getters/setters

```javascript

```

---

#### heran√ßa

```javascript

```
